						<p
							class='xsm:pt-[10px] xsm:pb-5 mb-0 pt-5 pb-[30px] text-black sm:pt-[10px] sm:pb-5 md:pt-[10px] md:pb-5 lg:pt-[10px] lg:pb-5 lg:text-xl/[30px] xl:text-xl/[30px]'>
							We turn your designs into production-ready Tailwind CSS, written to be easy to maintain, extend, and ship.
						</p>
						<ul class='mb-0 list-item list-none pl-0'>
							<li
								class='relative mb-5 pl-10 text-black before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:content-[url(../images/icon/icon_93.svg)] lg:text-xl/[30px] lg:text-[18px] xl:text-xl/[30px]'>
								Minimal custom CSS. Design tokens, spacing, and colors live in the Tailwind @theme where they belong.
							</li>
							<li
								class='relative mb-5 pl-10 text-black before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:content-[url(../images/icon/icon_93.svg)] lg:text-xl/[30px] lg:text-[18px] xl:text-xl/[30px]'>
