								(Chrome, Safari, Firefox, iOS Safari, Chrome Android)
							</li>
							<li
								class='relative mb-5 pl-10 text-black before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:content-[url(../images/icon/icon_93.svg)] lg:text-xl/[30px] lg:text-[18px] xl:text-xl/[30px]'>
								A ready-to-run project with all files included. Install dependencies and run locally with a single
								command.
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class='xxl:w-5/12 ml-auto! w-full max-w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-[12px] lg:w-6/12 xl:w-6/12'>
					<div class='mx-[-12px] flex flex-wrap items-end'>
						<div class='wow fadeInUp max-w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-[12px] sm:w-4/12 md:w-5/12 lg:w-5/12 xl:w-5/12'>
